'''碘乙酰胺'''（{{lang-en|Iodoacetamide}}）是一种[[烷基化试剂|烷基化试剂]]。与[[碘乙酸|碘乙酸]]类似，常用于封闭蛋白质[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]残基的[[巯基|巯基]]，防止重新形成[[二硫键|二硫键]]。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Smythe CV |title=The reactions of Iodoacetate and of Iodoacetamide with various Sulfhydryl groups, with Urease, and with Yeast preparations |journal=J. Biol. Chem. |volume=114 |issue=3 |pages=601–12 |year=1936 |url=http://www.jbc.org/content/114/3/601.full.pdf+html?sid=60fb7e03-5a4f-42fb-bd4e-3f86772cdc9d}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.1085/jgp.23.3.321 |author=Anson ML |title=The reactions of Iodine and Iodoacetamide with native Egg Albumin |journal=J. Gen. Physiol. |volume=23 |issue=3 |pages=321–31 |year=1940 |pmid=19873158 |pmc=2237930}}</ref> 
在[[泛素|泛素]]研究中，碘乙酰胺也被用来抑制{{link-en|泛素酶|Deubiquitinating enzyme}}(DUBs)。

